Package com.google.gxp.compiler.schema

Interface Summary
ContentFamilyVisitor<K,V> Visitor for ContentFamilys.
SchemaFactory Factory for creating/retrieving Schemas.
 

Class Summary
AttributeValidator Schema component which represents an XML attribute.
BuiltinSchemaFactory A SchemaFactory that can return all of the built-in Schemas
DelegatingSchemaFactory A SchemaFactory that can returns Schemas based on a collection of SchemaFactory delegates.
DocType Schema component which represents an XML doctype declaration (and possibly its SGML counterpart).
DuplicateContentTypeSchemaError An Alert caused when two different schemas with the same content-type are passed to gxpc.
ElementValidator Schema component which represents an XML element.
FileBackedSchemaFactory A SchemaFactory that can returns Schemas based on their locations within a supplied Filesystem.
Schema A Schema represents an output language like XHTML, RSS, VoiceXML or some other XML language that you might want to generate via GXP.
SchemaParser Parser for GXP schemas.
SchemaRef A reference to a Schema
 

Enum Summary
AttributeValidator.Flag Attribute flags.
ContentFamily An output content type.
ElementValidator.Flag Element flags.
